data.title: Bruce Willis, Kristen Stewart in Woody Allen's next
data.meta_description: Actors Bruce Willis, Kristen Stewart, Jesse Eisenberg and Blake Lively have come on board for veteran director Woody Allen's next film, which will go on the floors later this month.
